# Tailwind styling

- Use space tokens from `src/styles/tokens.css` via CSS variables.
- Prefer shadcn semantic utilities: `bg-background`, `text-primary`, `border-border`.
- **No** raw hex/rgb in TSX unless adding a new token in `tokens.css`.
- Marketing layout: `src/shared/ui/`. Interactive primitives: `src/components/ui/`.
